<h4>Activities offered:</h4>
<p style="font-size: 13px; font-family: arial, sans-serif;">
Roller Skating: Free style, Figure, Skate Ball, Roller Cricket<br/><br/>
Music: Singing and instrumental--Tabla and Keyboard in Indian Classical and western styles<br/><br/>
Dancing: Traditional, Contemporary, Bollywood, Salsa and Western styles<br/><br/>
Drawing: Basic Drawing, Coloring, Painting, Calligraphy, Mehndi<br/><br/>
Other:  Computer activities, Drama, Kindergarten and Spoken English<br/>
</p>
